{"tid":2440548,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"斥北京收緊選舉 只准應聲蟲治港  美跨黨促拜登行動撐港人","createTime":"2021-03-10T04:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T05:32:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b82c56d0f6bba6f064e8a6b0c31920e5bb4ad047","tid":2440548,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/6IHMZYLKZBHK7KWPUIIJAQMW5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2F6IHMZYLKZBHK7KWPUIIJAQMW5U%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplTkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=6c959cf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2F6IHMZYLKZBHK7KWPUIIJAQMW5U%2F&h=bd0d2e4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/6IHMZYLKZBHK7KWPUIIJAQMW5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n斥北京收緊選舉 只准應聲蟲治港 <br />\n美跨黨促拜登行動撐港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PqyyI_vDEjSBZA4vI7oPl5eE_Xo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W2HVGA7VWVD7XOIABJ6NYEVI3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPqyyI_vDEjSBZA4vI7oPl5eE_Xo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW2HVGA7VWVD7XOIABJ6NYEVI3A.jpg&h=f46c6b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國跨黨派議員發聲明，促拜登政府實踐已通過的法案維護香港自由。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京政府擬修改香港特首和立法會的選舉辦法，確保由「愛國者治港」，扼殺反對派的生存空間。美國參、眾兩院的外交委員會的跨黨派議員前日為此發聲明回應，批評北京試圖再收緊香港自治權，違反對國際社會的承諾，並提到他們過去兩年已通過法案，敦促拜登政府使用這些工具，與盟友和夥伴建立其他機構支持香港人。<br />\n<br />\n該份聲明獲多名國會重量級人馬支持，包括民主黨籍的參院外交委員會東亞小組主席馬基（Ed Markey）、小組資深成員兼共和黨元老羅姆尼（Mitt Romney）和民主黨籍的眾院外交事務委員會亞洲小組主席貝拉（Ami Bera），旨在譴責人大計劃明日表決增加香港選舉制度的限制。<br />\n<br />\n他們表示十分關注相關修訂，認為這。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他們承諾美國議會將繼續一致地。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜發言人就北。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8cst-wGETJaunRzCi9UWySKGVgE=/802x671/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4RO2QVCWARB6HA6LJTXCIO4FE4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8cst-wGETJaunRzCi9UWySKGVgE%3D%2F802x671%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4RO2QVCWARB6HA6LJTXCIO4FE4.png&h=9c1228aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指審訊不公 學者籲律師勿赴港<br />\n<br />\n另外，聯合國人權理事會日前召開第46次會議，出席會議的國際律師協會人權研究所總監Helena Kennedy發言時批評中國打壓人權，不應自稱有法治，批評國安法下公平審訊不受保障，包括有案件不設陪審團，並由指定法官審理，「法治是由獨立法官、律師處理案件」，又指若大律師公會甚至法官私下表達憂慮，相信相關意見會被重視。<br />\n<br />\n她又說會鼓勵普通法國家不再。。。。。。"},{"pid":"484ca32eb15066d050c351c5d6d71a951c14ffc3","tid":2440548,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"又指若大律師公會甚至法官私下表達憂慮，相信相關意見會被重視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7360d61b5531bba1570a5e21057f780ec5dcc0","tid":2440548,"uid":258903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"乜action都好<br />\n比d action睇睇<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"90851f19e625af14df80c6ba2a30feb1471d642a","tid":2440548,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ea21a2fbe8eb802defac8ea8e44279fc86cf13","tid":2440548,"uid":46388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"香港又唔係黑人